{
  "stem": "8842.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought us into our city where we lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I understood then that they brought us into a school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't remember which school it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was a school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And parents start coming in to pick us up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My oldest sister came to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Running through the streets until we got to our house was an unbelievable experience because bombs kept on falling in the streets, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a nonstop, violent bombing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by the time-- by the time we came home, my mother and father were completely destroyed, not knowing what's happening with us until we got-- because there were no telephone communications in those days.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we didn't even have a telephone in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we finally got together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the family was together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they tried to explain to me that this is the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what are we going to do about it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, we'll have to try to run away because if this is what's happening, the Germans will come here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they will do to us the same thing what they did to the Polish people in Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you know anything beyond that they had to move?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Did you know-- had you heard anything about what was happening to the Jews?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Poland?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very vaguely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very vaguely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents positively knew-- no, without any doubt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe my older sister knew more about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was four years older then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was, like--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--15--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--16, going to 16.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she knew much more about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Either they tried to close, you know, to cover up for the younger two daughters, or-- I didn't know really the impact of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the second morning, we were all packed up.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
